      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，就是起点指向Active，Active也能回到终点。那Active内部还需要细分吗？比如有没有子状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Active是个复合状态，里面有两个并行的处理流程，一个叫Process1，一个叫Process2。它们各自从Active内部的初始状态开始，而且是并行运行的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Process1",
        "Process2",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Active作为父状态，内部有两个子状态Process1和Process2，各自都有独立的初始入口，这两条线是并行的关系，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Process1",
        "Process2",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是并行结构。两个流程独立启动，没有先后依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Process1",
        "Process2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我用stateDiagram-v2来画。先建Active这个复合状态，里面放Process1和Process2，各自从内部起点连过去，然后外部起点连到Active，Active再连到外部终点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "stateDiagram-v2",
        "Active",
